# CODEOWNERS
#
# This file defines who is responsible for reviewing code in different parts of the repository.
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners (GitHub usernames or team names).
#
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global owners - will be requested for review on all PRs unless a more specific match exists
* @your-org/admins

# Frontend code
/src/ @your-org/frontend-team
/public/ @your-org/frontend-team
/components/ @your-org/frontend-team
/pages/ @your-org/frontend-team
/styles/ @your-org/frontend-team
*.tsx @your-org/frontend-team
*.jsx @your-org/frontend-team
*.css @your-org/frontend-team
*.scss @your-org/frontend-team
package.json @your-org/frontend-team

# Backend code
/api/ @your-org/backend-team
/services/ @your-org/backend-team
/models/ @your-org/backend-team
/controllers/ @your-org/backend-team
/routes/ @your-org/backend-team
/middleware/ @your-org/backend-team
/database/ @your-org/backend-team
*.sql @your-org/backend-team

# Infrastructure and DevOps
/terraform/ @your-org/infra-team
/kubernetes/ @your-org/infra-team
/docker/ @your-org/infra-team
/.github/ @your-org/infra-team
/scripts/ @your-org/infra-team
Dockerfile @your-org/infra-team
docker-compose.yml @your-org/infra-team
*.tf @your-org/infra-team
*.yaml @your-org/infra-team
*.yml @your-org/infra-team

# Configuration files - require additional review from admins
.env.example @your-org/admins @your-org/infra-team
*.config.js @your-org/admins
*.config.ts @your-org/admins

# Security-sensitive files - require security team review
/secrets/ @your-org/security-team @your-org/admins
*.key @your-org/security-team @your-org/admins
*.pem @your-org/security-team @your-org/admins
*.p12 @your-org/security-team @your-org/admins

# Documentation - can be reviewed by anyone, but notify docs team
*.md @your-org/docs-team
/docs/ @your-org/docs-team

# CI/CD workflows - require both infra and admins review
/.github/workflows/ @your-org/infra-team @your-org/admins

# Database migrations - require backend and DBA review
/migrations/ @your-org/backend-team @your-org/dba-team
/db/migrations/ @your-org/backend-team @your-org/dba-team

# Testing - require QA team review
/tests/ @your-org/qa-team
/test/ @your-org/qa-team
*.test.ts @your-org/qa-team
*.test.js @your-org/qa-team
*.spec.ts @your-org/qa-team
*.spec.js @your-org/qa-team

# Package dependencies - require security review for changes
package-lock.json @your-org/security-team @your-org/backend-team
yarn.lock @your-org/security-team @your-org/frontend-team
requirements.txt @your-org/security-team @your-org/backend-team
Gemfile.lock @your-org/security-team @your-org/backend-team
go.mod @your-org/security-team @your-org/backend-team
go.sum @your-org/security-team @your-org/backend-team
